/2019/03/nicolas-cage-will-kick-some-serious-ass-in-the-new-martial-arts-film-jiu-jitsu-contrib.html|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2019-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326134444/https://screenanarchy.com/2019/03/nicolas-cage-will-kick-some-serious-ass-in-the-new-martial-arts-film-jiu-jitsu-contrib.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Vorel|first=Jim|title=Nic Cage to Fight Aliens with His Bare Hands in Jiu Jitsu|date=2019-03-20|publisher=Paste|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/nicolas-cage/nic-cage-to-fight-aliens-with-his-bare-hands-in-ji/|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007125717/https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/nicolas-cage/nic-cage-to-fight-aliens-with-his-bare-hands-in-ji/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Beans|first=Freddy|title=Nicolas Cage gets wrapped up in JIU JITSU|date=2019-03-20|publisher=Ain't It Cool News|url=https://www.aintitcool.com/nicolas-cage-gets-wrapped-up-in-jiu-jitsu-81912/|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321171626/https://www.aintitcool.com/nicolas-cage-gets-wrapped-up-in-jiu-jitsu-81912/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月，[[法蘭克·葛里洛|法蘭克·葛里洛]]、[[東尼嘉|東尼嘉]]、[[陳鈺芸|陳鈺芸]]、[[瑪麗·艾格洛浦路斯|瑪麗·艾格洛浦路斯]]和[[尹成植_(演員)|尹成植]]加入演出陣容<ref name="Deadline(2019-06-06)">{{cite web|last=Pedersen|first=Erik|title=‘Jiu Jitsu’: Frank Grillo, Rick Yune, Tony Jaa & Others Joins Nicolas Cage Martial Arts Pic|date=2019-06-06|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/jiu-jistu-frank-grillo-rick-yune-tony-jaa-others-join-nicolas-cage-action-movie-1202628433/|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816232848/https://deadline.com/2019/06/jiu-jistu-frank-grillo-rick-yune-tony-jaa-others-join-nicolas-cage-action-movie-1202628433/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2019年6月在[[賽普勒斯|賽普勒斯]]開始進行<ref>{{cite web|author=[[Associated_Press|Associ