== 發行 ==
《柔道煞星》由{{lang|en|The Avenue Entertainment}}定於2020年11月20日在美國以[[隨選視訊|VOD]]和[[DVD首映|DVD首映]]的方式發行<ref>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Avenue Entertainment Launching With Nicolas Cage’s ‘Jiu Jitsu’|date=2020-09-09|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/avenue-entertainment-launching-nicolas-cage-jiu-jitsu-1234763858/|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911165511/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/avenue-entertainment-launching-nicolas-cage-jiu-jitsu-1234763858/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在其首周末，該片在[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]上租借量排名第八，在[[Fandango_(公司)|FandangoNow]]上排名第九。<ref name=Brueggemann-Sept2020 />

